{"tid":291926,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雲加：一早有VAR我就贏歐聯啦","createTime":"2017-06-21T03:05:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-21T05:47:43.000Z","uid":46892,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5bf1bc36ccbfee19e0338a9595f464282035e09d","tid":291926,"uid":46892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T03:05:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=JydjAett6ydDo5rJC82wtpUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=9503b4bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】視像助理裁判（VAR）乃近期球壇熱話，阿仙奴領隊雲加認為，如果一早推行這個科技執法，歐聯冠軍早應到手。<br />\n<br />\n國際足協於本屆洲際國家盃全面採用VAR，其中日前智利對喀麥隆的比賽，VAR兩番發揮作用，影響球證判決，成為一時熱話。阿仙奴領隊雲加對於新科技趨之若騖，亦表明若一早採用VAR，他不致未贏過歐聯冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n他特別提到2006年阿仙奴對巴塞隆拿的決賽，最需要VAR：「我會說巴塞隆拿2006年歐聯決賽扳平的一球，因為那是越位，我們那時在餘下30分鐘領先1:0。那是我錯失的錦標，是最重要的一個。」他正色道，顯然仍對當年一戰耿耿於懷。<br />\n<br />\n那年決賽，阿仙奴在領先下被伊度奧扳平，那正是雲加口中的越位球。及後，比列堤為巴塞奠勝，令阿仙奴飲恨。"},{"pid":"ae62e00edd120a963d24e0c1f67fc03e4ab92708","tid":291926,"uid":46892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T03:06:06.000Z","msg":"雲加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"993e12d0d1d500d292a6efe48599beaa168f5d9f","tid":291926,"uid":14486,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T03:07:56.000Z","msg":"有VAR你俾人炒左啦"},{"pid":"c980f6f5325838afd62915b453a4b22d2835d4e0","tid":291926,"uid":25230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T03:09:17.000Z","msg":"雲加：有VAR我洗輸？"},{"pid":"f20eaf3ff6c25cb889e48c54d560d45e03e2977f","tid":291926,"uid":34178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T03:09:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97c9c790125a251ae98be36be9c621a55cb3fb26","tid":291926,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T03:11:38.000Z","msg":"呢鋪撐個死老野，果場波我唔開心左好耐，之後仲要冇埋亨利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},